  ('social-worker-moex-00506', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'essay', '懷孕期的照護提供，對懷孕的女性及其胎兒都很重要，根據 Perloff 及
