  ('social-worker-moex-00507', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '學齡期或青少年早期的兒少，為獲得旁人讚美而表現之行為，應屬Kohlberg道德推理理論的那個 階段？', '["道德循規前期（pre-conventionallevel）的第一階段", "道德循規前期（pre-conventionallevel）的第二階段", "道德循規期（conventionallevel）的第三階段", "道德循規期（conventionallevel）的第四階段"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d58af1a12be8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e55234e27b63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00508', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', 'ErikErikson心理社會發展理論關於中年期的發展任務，下列敘述何者正確？', '["學習一技之長，期待能夠找到工作", "進入戀愛關係，尋找伴侶", "回顧過去，感覺人生圓滿", "主動和他人接觸，指引未來的世代"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d58af1a12be8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e55234e27b63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-00509', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-112-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關Piaget認知發展理論的感覺運動期，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["反射動作（reflexactivity）：父母手指碰觸孩子的小手，孩子自然抓住", "主要循環反應（primarycircularreactions）：發現有舒適感、開始吸手指", "三級循環反應（tertiarycircularreactions）：看到大人拍手，會跟著拍手，但無法主動拍手", "具象思維（representationalthought）：快樂的時候會主動拍手"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d58af1a12be8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e55234e27b63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
